2005-12-20  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* SkunkWeb/Services/mvc/__init__.py: adding misnamed mvc service
	(m and v are missing).

2005-09-20  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/skunk/computils.py: convenience functions for dealing
	with AE.

2005-09-14  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* SkunkWeb/Services/templating/UrlBuilder.py: url function now htmlquotes.

2005-08-16  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/AE/Cache.py (_fixPath): fix for docroot escaping.

2005-05-10  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@bracknell.smullyan.org>

	* SkunkWeb/Services/sessionHandler/PsycopgSessionStore.py:
	adding (contributed by Nick Murtagh).

2005-04-18  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>
	
	* pylibs/formlib/validates.py (COUNTRY_CODES): typo fix for
	American Samoa.

2005-04-17  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/SocketMan/SocketMan.py: now, rather than hard-coding `5'
	as the argument to listen(), use socket.SOMAXCONN, which is
	much more than 5 on many platforms.

	* SkunkWeb/Services/requestHandler/requestHandler.py
	(_processRequest): typo in error handling (backport from skunk4).

2005-04-07  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* SkunkWeb/SkunkWeb/Server.py (SkunkWebServer.run): fix for
	seteuid and setgid.  There was previously a guard in place to undo
	any seteuid before calling setuid, but not before calling
	setgid. (Backport from skunk4.)

2005-04-13  Andrew Csillag  <drew@localhost.localdomain>

	* SkunkWeb/util/precompile.py.in: now sets runOutOfCache to 0.
	Obviously, if you are precompiling, running out of the cache makes
	absolutely zero sense.

2005-03-08  Andrew Csillag  <drew@localhost.localdomain>

	* pylibs/DT/DTLexer.py: fix so that when encountering <<:, the
	lexer would still find the begin tag.
	
2005-01-31  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/AE/mime.types: adding mime type for XUL documents.

2005-01-11  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/jsutils.py (_dict_to_js): for some reason, was improperly
	marshalling dictionaries.

2004-10-01  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/PyDO/PyDO.py (PyDOBase.get): get() for some reason had
	crazy semantics; now is equivalent to obj.dict().get().

2004-09-10  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* SkunkWeb/configure, SkunkWeb/configure.in: added psycopgcache
	module to list of services.

	* pylibs/PsycopgCache.py: adding cache module.

	* SkunkWeb/Services/psycopgcache.py: adding cache service.

	* pylibs/PyDO/psycopgconn.py (PyDOPostgreSQL.__init__): fixed
	various fatal bugs.

2004-09-02  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/AE/Cache.py (_fixPath): this has gone through various
	incarnations, and the last one appears to be broken again. I think
	this works.

	* pylibs/DT/DT.py (DT.__call__): don't use locals() mutably for
	store/unstore, use a dict.

2004-07-28  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/AE/Component.py (ComponentStackFrame.__del__):
	removing the __del__ method, as Python now can take care of circular
	references without help.

2004-07-25  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/DT/DTLexer.py: pcre has finally been removed from Python
	in 2.4a1; I rewrote this to use the re module.  

2004-05-26  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* SkunkWeb/Services/psyco_accel.py: simplest possible service that
	invokes psyco.  Will probably be jazzed up a bit.

2004-05-12  Drew Csillag  <drew_csillag@yahoo.com>

	* SkunkWeb/util/precompile.py.in: now compiles message catalogs too

2004-04-09  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/DT/DTLexer.py (findTags): now allows files to end
	in "<".

2004-04-05  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/AE/Cache.py: when checking for change of a file, now return
	the max of ctime and mtime, to support smbfs shares where the ctime
	isn't updated correctly.

2004-03-18  Drew Csillag  <drew@loki.sai.local>

	* pylibs/SocketMan/SocketMan.py (SocketMan.retrying_bind): added
	retrying_bind so can call with either UNIX or TCP socket for the
	retry stuff

2004-03-17  Drew Csillag  <drew@loki.sai.local>

	* SkunkWeb/util/precompile.py.in: now when creating shadow
	directories, it will copy non-compilable things, and copy symlinks
	(not what they point to) to the shadow directory.

2004-03-15  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/SocketMan/SocketMan.py (SocketMan.addConnection): now
	break out of the retry loop if the socket bind succeeds.

2004-03-15  Drew Csillag <drew@loki.sai.local>

	* pylibs/SocketMan/SocketMan.py (SocketMan.addConnection): now
	retries a few times on bind in case the original isn't quite dead
	yet.

	* SkunkWeb/SkunkWeb/LogObj.py (redirectStdOutErr): now checks to
	see if stderr/stdout already redirected before redirecting again
	
	* SkunkWeb/skunkweb.py.in: now logs the exception *before* writing
	that skunkweb died abnormally so that you actually get to see the
	exception if writing to stderr fails.  Also logs any exception if
	we get the "server exited wayyy too soon" message.

2004-03-14  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/xmlutils.py (XMLElement.__eq__, __ne__): added rich
	comparison methods for testing equality; fix for AttributeError.

2004-03-12  Jacob Smullyan <smulloni@smullyan.org>
	* pylibs/PyDO/PyDO2.py: removed use of string module
	in favor of string methods (stylistic nit-pick).

2004-03-02 Drew Csillag <drew@loki.sai.local>
	
	* SkunkWeb/Services/sessionHandler/FSSessionStore.py: removed one
	of the two leading underscores from get/setPickle

	* SkunkWeb/Services/auth/__init__.py (SessionAuthBase): now you
	can pass path, domain and secure to the constructor to set the 
	appropriate parameters on the session cookie

2004-03-01  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* SkunkWeb/sw.conf.in (HTTPKeepaliveTimeout): document new default
	value for HTTPKeepaliveTimeout.

	* SkunkWeb/Services/httpd/__init__.py: setting default value of
	HTTPKeepaliveTimeout to 0 rather than 15.

2004-02-27    <drew@loki.sai.local>

	* SkunkWeb/sw.conf.in: added documentation of dontCacheSource,
	noTagDebug and runOutOfCache options

	* SkunkWeb/util/precompile.py.in: now can compile individual files
	and also deletes the cache file before compiling (otherwise if the
	timestamp isn't newer, it wouldn't recompile)

2004-02-26    <drew@loki.sai.local>

	* pylibs/SkunkExcept.py (SkunkSyntaxError.format): fix so that
	doing things like <:args `foo`:> don't totally bomb, but you get a
	reasonble error.

