	an OSError occurs.

	* SkunkWeb/Services/sessionHandler/fssession_clean.sh: session
	cleaner script made to work nicely with AE Cache sessions.

	* SkunkWeb/Services/sessionHandler/AECacheSessionStore.py
	(Store.delete): now delete the session file rather than "expiring"
	it.

