	* pylibs/hooks.py (KeyedHook.oneshot, Hook.oneshot): added
	"oneshot" methods, where a hook function will be executed just
	once and then removed.

	* pylibs/formlib/aecomp.py (ComponentSubmitProcessor): added new
	class that wraps a component call in a function in a trivial way.

