	* SkunkWeb/Services/templating/SafeSpoolTag.py: modified to use
	DT.DTCompilerUtil.safe_import.

	* pylibs/DT/DTCompilerUtil.py (safe_import): added utility
	function for importing a module into the hidden namespace.
	(Output.writelines): utility function for writing several lines
	with one function call.

