	and comments thereon.

2003-04-19  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/AE/MsgCatalog.py,
	SkunkWeb/Services/templating/MailServices.py,
	SkunkWeb/Services/ae_component.py, pylibs/AE/MimeTypes.py,
	pylibs/AE/Executables.py, pylibs/AE/Component.py,
	pylibs/AE/Cache.py: changed method names to be compatible with
	Scopeable.

	* pylibs/ConfigLoader.py (loadConfig): now use scope.Scopeable
	directly, without the silly subclass.

	* pylibs/scope.py: a new implementation, much faster (by an order
	of ten or more) than the old for attribute lookups.

2003-04-18  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* SkunkWeb/Services/usertracking.py (_add_usertracking_cookie):
	fix for cookie expiration.

	* SkunkWeb/SkunkWeb/Server.py (_setConfigDefaults): setting default
	value for runInForeground here, not in bootloader.py.

	* SkunkWeb/SkunkWeb/bootloader.py.in (init): the default value for
	runInForeground shouldn't be set here.

	* pylibs/scope.py: added "freeze" and "unfreeze" methods
	that store the scoped values in self.__dict__ and clean them
	out, respectively. (deleted this later.)
	(Scopeable.pop): made compatible with scopeable.Scopeable.pop().

