	* pylibs/ConfigLoader.py: switch to using the Python version of
	scope.

2003-04-17  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/scope.py: The Python version turns out to be, with a
	couple of small optimizations, 33% faster than the C version. 

