	* pylibs/PostgreSql/__init__.py (SimpleQueryTest): added
	connection_test capability to verify connections (useful
	if the database is being accessed remotely and connections
	are liable to intermittently going south).

	* SkunkWeb/SkunkWeb/Server.py (start): removing "server starting"
	message that I don't want to see any more. 
	
2003-04-02  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* SkunkWeb/swpython.py.in (usage): added "-q", "--quiet" options
	to suppress the "Initializing..." message that I'm tired of
	seeing.

	* SkunkWeb/swmgr.in: You can now stop or restart the daemon
	without running swpython if you pass swmgr the "-f" option (and if
	your pid file is in the configured default, which is likely); also
	improved usage text a tad.

