	* test/sitelibs/formlibtest/testDispatch3.py
	(PushyFlowManager.getStartForm): fixed to match signature change
	in dispatcher.py.

2003-01-01  James Richards  <jrichards@satie.wnyc.org>

	* views.py (ViewableCompositeField.__init__): Overriding setting
	of fields attribute to use ViewableFieldProxies instead of
	FieldProxies
	
	(ViewableFieldProxy.__init__): Added ViewableFieldProxy class to
	override viewable name of proxied fields in output xhtml
	
	(isviewable): added isviewable utility function to simplify checks
	for viewable objects during form layouts, etc...moved Layout
	subclasses to use new utility method

	* form.py (Form.setData): added explicit check for composite field
	and iteration over composite fields during data setting
	(CompositeField.__init__): changed components property to be named
	fields to simplify interactions with layout objects also added
	errors list for same reason....NOTE, it may be better to handle
	absence of error property in layout objects, not certain which
	approach is best..minor issue for now

	* testCompositeField.pyinc (cmpFld): Added more debugging output
	to track composite field values

