	components
	

2002-11-26 Jacob Smullyan   <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* test/formlib/htdocs/testNestedList.pyinc: added some debug output.

	* pylibs/formlib/form.py (Field.__init__): fields now have a "setable"
	attribute; if a field is setable, it will be nulled out if you setData
	on a form containing it with a dictionary that doesn't include its 
	fieldname.  Hidden fields and submit inputs are not setable.
	(DomainField.in_domain): handle None and (currently) [None]; the latter
	shouldn't be the value returned for multiple field that hasn't gotten 
	a submission -- it should be either None or [] -- but that is what it is
	at the moment.

	* pylibs/formlib/views.py (_requirable.validate): hack-type fix
	for required fields.

	* pylibs/formlib/dispatcher.py (FormDispatcher.dispatch): 
	pass state to next().

	* pylibs/formlib/views.py (ViewableForm.__init__): added processors
	argument.

	* test/formlib/htdocs/testDispatch2.{html,pyinc}: new test
	which does some conditional dispatching.

2002-11-25  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* test/formlib/htdocs/testDispatch1.html: first dispatcher test.

	* test/formlib/htdocs/testAllViews.pyinc: cosmetic changes.
	
	* pylibs/formlib/dispatcher.py, pylibs/formlib/state.py: various
	bugfixes.
	
	* pylibs/formlib/__init__.py: import all from everything.

2002-11-25  Jacob Smullyan  <jsmullyan@wnyc.org>

	* pylibs/formlib/views.py: wrapped some long lines.

2002-11-25  Jacob Smullyan <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/formlib/views.py (ViewableForm.handleError): made it
	work with FormError lists.

	* pylibs/formlib/validates.py: changed the validation routines
	to use FormError lists.

	* pylibs/formlib/form.py (Form.validate): errors is now a
	FieldContainer storing lists of FormErrors for every field.

	* pylibs/formlib/views.py (ViewableForm.getView): made form view
	work with a list of errors returned for a field rather than a
	single one. 

	* pylibs/formlib/dispatcher.py (LinearFlowManager.next): removed
	unnecessary End class, and permit a Goto with a null formname.

	* test/formlib/htdocs/test{1-4}.pyinc: changed value view_attr to
	default in several places; changed validation to use FormErrors.

2002-11-24  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/vfs/pickleProps.py: several typo corrections.

2002-11-24  James Richards  <jrichards@satie.wnyc.org>

	* test/formlib/htdocs/testValidates.pyinc: added test for required
	IntField, DoubleField and DateField

	* test/formlib/htdocs/testAllViews.pyinc: added tests of required
	fields for TextField and ButtonGroupField

	* pylibs/formlib/views.py (ViewableField.__init__): added raising
	of ValueError if 'value' key is present in view_attrs: setting
	value on a Viewable item during construction conflicts with the
	notion of a default value and introduces programmer confusion into
	the forms API

	* pylibs/formlib/__init__.py: added import of all from validates
	module

	* pylibs/formlib/validates.py: added superclass validation check
	to IntField, DoubleField and DateField

	* pylibs/formlib/views.py: added support for required fields to
	ViewableField and ViewableDomainField
	

