	* docs/tutorial/src/: (various files) some progress on 'hoptime'
	demo application.
	* SkunkWeb/Services/auth/__init__.py (CookieAuthBase.login): login
	now returns what validate returns to it if the value is true.
	This is useful when validate returns a User object of some kind.

