	documentation about the abs argument to <:url:>.

	* SkunkWeb/Services/templating/UrlBuilder.py (_genUrl): fixed url
	generation so it handles "need_full" argument correctly; now
	handles https and relies less on the presence of the Host request
	header. 

	* SkunkWeb/Services/templating/HTMLTags.py (UrlTag.genCode): added
	new argument, "abs", which generates an absolute url when true.

