	* pylibs/PyDO/postconn.py (_dateConvertFromDB): module was broken,
	at least with postgresql 7.2.2, when the timestamp returned contained
	milliseconds but no timezone.
	
2002-09-29  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/xmlrpchandler.py: helper module for writing XMLRPC servers. 

