2002-08-30  Jacob Smullyan  <jsmullyan@wnyc.org>

	* pylibs/flowmgr/flowdef.dtd: DTD for flow definitions.

	* pylibs/xmlutils.py (XMLElement.__init__): made attributes
	dictionary directly available and non-private.

2002-08-29  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/xmlutils.py (makeElement): modified parser so it could
	produce different element classes depending on element name and
	elementClassRegistry. (XMLElement.getChildrenByAttribute): moved
	this here from ecs.xhtml; also added method aliases getElement,
	getElements, getElementsByAttribute.

	* pylibs/ecs/xhtml.py (parse): added parse method that returns
	a tree of Elements given an xhtml string.

2002-08-28  Jacob Smullyan  <jsmullyan@wnyc.org>

	* pylibs/xmlutils.py (XMLElement.__str__): now adds spaces in
	empty elements for user-agent compatibility with xhtml.

	* pylibs/ecs/__init__.py, xhtml.py: An ECS-clone for Python.  Uses
	xmlutils.  Now I need to add a parser, and support comments, etc.

