2002-08-08  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/PyDO/sqliteconn.py (PyDOSqlite.execute): added some
	debugging. Until the next version of pysqlite is released, this
	won't work, as the current version returns the wrong value for
	rowcount.  PySQLite in CVS at least exposes the necessary portion
	of the C API for me to find the correct value for rowcount after
	an INSERT/UPDATE, but I have only tested with 2.0, the last
	release. 
