2002-01-09  Jacob Smullyan  <smulloni@smullyan.org>

	* pylibs/vfs/zipfs.py, parfs.py: VFS tweaks.

	* SkunkWeb/sample_webdocs/demo/gallery/index.html: added image
	gallery demo (requires Python Imaging Library).

